Corporate Responsibility > 
Climate risk and environmental impacts > 
Products and services




Products and services







Through our products and services we aim to protect our customers against the impacts of climate change and minimise the environmental impact of our claims process.





Green products





Aviva creates products that support our customers when they make environmentally responsible choices, like reduced premium motor insurance for customers using public transport or generating their own renewable electricity. We offered 16 similar products globally in 2016. 







Energy efficient replacement goods






Aviva is providing energy efficient replacements to help reduce customers' energy costs in the long-term. 
 


Find out more about Energy efficient replacement goods
 
					







Making things good as new






We’re working with restoration specialists to restore more of our customers' items and reduce the environmental impacts of replacing them.


Find out more about Making things good as new
 
					








